dc_description_s: This polygon feature class represents boundaries of the 72 counties in Wisconsin. The data is derived from 1:24,000-scale sources. This feature class was last updated in June 2015; refer to the Data Lineage section of the ArcGIS metadata for information about the nature of the update. For more information, contact the WI DNR Bureau of Technology Services.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit:https://data-wi-dnr.opendata.arcgis.com/datasets/county-boundaries-24k
